{"name":"Roberto Rastapopoulos","nameCn":"拉斯泰波波罗斯","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/f0/67/25386_crt_DBbBP.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>拉斯泰波波罗斯</li>","detail":"又译拉普洛斯，首次出现于《丁丁在美洲》。《丁丁历险记》中的大反派，在数个故事中都有登场，表面身份为彬彬有礼的电影大亨（甚至在《奇怪的雪茄》中伪装帮助过丁丁），但不久就逐渐暴露出毒品贩子的真实身份。尽管每次都以被丁丁挫败而收场，但仗着“坏蛋活千年”，这位大鼻子匪首总能总能死里逃生东山再起，他是丁丁最难缠的对手之一，和他的斗争也贯穿了全故事系列的主线。他的结局是被外星生物带入不明飞行物而失踪，但是他在《丁丁与字母艺术》中他以一个邪教教主和假艺术品贩子的身份出现，并试图将丁丁做成一个名为“凯撒”的膨胀雕塑，使得丁丁在这部未完成作品中留下了他的生死悬念。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/105759","name":"Tintin and the lake of sharks","nameCn":"丁丁在鲨鱼湖","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/cd/76/105759_us.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":1},{"href":"/subject/105732","name":"The Red Sea Sharks (The Adventures of Tintin)","nameCn":"红海鲨鱼","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/65/a6/105732_us.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":1},{"href":"/subject/105717","name":"Cigars of the Pharoah (The Adventures of Tintin)","nameCn":"法老的雪茄","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/52/d6/105717_us.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":1},{"href":"/subject/56759","name":"The Adventures of Tintin Season 3","nameCn":"丁丁历险记 第三季","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/0f/4f/56759_79bLQ.jpg","staff":"客串","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":2},{"href":"/subject/56758","name":"The Adventures of Tintin Season 2","nameCn":"丁丁历险记第二季","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d1/d9/56758_c0ccf.jpg","staff":"客串","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":2},{"href":"/subject/56757","name":"The Adventures of Tintin Season 1","nameCn":"丁丁历险记第一季","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/91/06/56757_648N5.jpg","staff":"客串","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":2},{"href":"/subject/105718","name":"The Blue Lotus (The Adventures of Tintin)","nameCn":"蓝莲花","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/68/35/105718_us.jpg","staff":"客串","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover"